data.description: Nestled in a quiet section of the highly coveted Lake Forest subdivision, this charming home offers the best of suburban living combined with modern amenities.   Features: • Fortified roof: See attached documents for certificate.  • Well-Designed Layout: A single-story home with 3 sizable bedrooms, 2 full baths spanning an approximate living area of 1,470 sq ft.  • Warm and Inviting Living Space: The living room, measuring 14.5 X 18.5 with vaulted ceilings and a cozy wood burning fireplace, serves as the heart of the home, making it perfect for relaxation and family gatherings.  • Gourmet Kitchen: Fully equipped with essential appliances like a dishwasher, microwave, range-electric, refrigerator with an ice maker, and more. Enjoy casual dining in the breakfast nook with dimensions 10 X 9.  • Master Suite Oasis: The primary bedroom, located on the main level, boasts dimensions of 11.5 X 17.5 and features a double vanity, garden tub, walk-in closet, vaulted ceilings, ensuring a comfortable and luxurious living experience.  • Outdoor Features: A screened porch provides a serene outdoor relaxation spot. Coupled with a fenced property, and a double garage with an automatic garage door, the exterior amenities of this property are tailored for convenience.  • Community Perks: As a resident of Lake Forest, indulge in amenities such as the clubhouse, pool, and a golf course. The monthly association fee of $60 ensures that these facilities are well-maintained for your enjoyment.  • Additional Features: Central electric heating/cooling, composition shingle roofing, a fortifying roof for added protection, brick and vinyl exterior finish for durability, and more.  • Ideal Investment: This property is also suitable for long-term rentals.
